title: Maginon Supra IPC-1 IPCameraConfig software.
description:
Here you can find the SupraIPConfig software and user manual for your Maginon Supra IPC-1 IP-camera. If you don't have this camera, do not download this.

Language:  Italian, Hungarian, Dutch and Slovanian. Other languages can be downloaded at http://www.supra-elektronik.com

I upload this because you can't download the software 'IPCameraConfig' from the site of Maginon, only user manuals and firmware's.
